summary.caption: “Frankie! When didja get out? … Gee, I bet you been sittin’ in da cage wonderin’ where me and da loot wuz!  … Oh, Frankie, Frankie … heh heh heh … Want some coffee, Frankie?”

summary.caption: “I tell you he’s up there! … Those wild, sunken eyes! That horrid wooden leg! … And he’s looking for me!”
